# Installing spark on Linux (Ubuntu 16.04)
* source *Apache Spark*, Aven J. 

## Prerequisites
* 8 GB or more memory
* Eight or more CPU cores
* 10 GB or greater network speed
* Four or more disks in JBOD configuration
* Java installed
* Python installed

## Downloading pre-built packages. 
* spark.apache.org/downloads.html
* choose a Spark release.  I downloaded 2.2.1
* package type = Prebuilt for Hadoop 2.7
* Click on the tar file to start the download. 
 - You can also use wget or curl
